content: I don’t understand people. They have complained about Obamacare since it started. Now that someone wants to do something better, hopefully, all they want to do is gripe. I guess it is because Pres. Trump is at the head of the table if it was a Dem. that would be. Hillary’s people need to get over it, let Pres. Trump have his time to “make America great again”.
